title: Let The Legends 55+ Living Sweep You Off Your Feet With a 2 BR Apt!
map_address: 570 Settlers Ridge Parkway near Hudson Rd
posting_body: ['The Legends of Woodbury, located near all of the local shop and dining hot spots, will provide you everything you are looking for in a luxurious 55+ apartment home.', 'This community provides one, two and three bedroom options as well as many different floor plans for all three arrangements.', 'Here, you are not only spoiled in your own home with high ceilings, stunning kitchen appliances and countertops and large walk-in closets, but we also spoil you with the community itself.', 'The Legends of Woodbury provides our residents with a theater room, card and craft room, a fully-equipped fitness center, a community room, a beautiful outdoor seating area and even heated garage parking.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is also a pet-friendly community.', 'In addition, we have an area to even let your furry friends run around outside!', 'If you haven’t fallen in love with the Legends of Woodbury yet, let our on-site management team answer your questions for you!', 'NOTE: Office Hours - By Appointment Only.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- Card & Crafts Room', '- Close to Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Coffee Shops & More!', '- 2-Story Clubhouse', '- Outdoor Dog Run', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a community for active seniors that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'At least one household member must be at least 55 years of age.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Woodbury', '570 Settlers Ridge Parkway', 'Woodbury, MN, 55129', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'M4UDup6qAvQ']
